snippet.title: Ys X: Nordics - Announcement Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, PC)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/ys-x/

A boundless sea of adventure and discovery awaits you in Ys X: Nordics!

Join Adol Christin and his unlikely ally, the pirate Karja Balta, as they learn to work together to save the people of Obelia Gulf from the mysterious immortal monsters known as the Griegers. Exhilarating, fast-paced combat, a moving story of unexpected bonds, and naval exploration await you!

Coming Fall 2024 to Nintendo Switch™, PS4®, PS5®, and PC!

#YsX #YsXNordics
